, "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 61}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果象棋的棋子都由真人扮演，被吃掉就会死，那么扮演哪个棋子相对而言最安全？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "假设你是一个士兵，有一个残暴的国王命令你们每人扮演一枚棋子，进行一场真人象棋比赛，由两名棋手对弈，被吃掉的棋子会立刻被处决，那么扮演哪个棋子是最安全的呢？ 补充说明： 1. 将和帅在输掉对局时会被处决，其他棋子被吃掉的情况下会被处决。 2. 两名棋手都是国手级的高手，实力相当，但红方先行。假设两人不知道自己的对局会导致士兵死亡，因此对局不受干扰。 3. 士兵必须遵守规则不能乱跑，可以假设周围有监军，不遵守规则就会杀掉换人。 看了大家的回答，看来答案还是比较明显的，考虑到和棋的可能性，将帅起码有 50% 以上概率存活，那么本问题其实已经解决了，不过除了将帅以外的棋子可能还有一定讨论空间。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-95e84ed6ca3a1e0d29d0b7af07ae05f9_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "168 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/601853961"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IgMCpq7izivBAEAMaCDk2MDI1NzQ5IMHbm6MGMAQ4fEAEcgk2MDE4NTM5NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1684509038.4826045", "card_id": "Q_440200131", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 346}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在的房子都建二三十层高，将来房龄到了，老房子该怎么处理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8c5816f3fe23f1b66bf3c78853b5e91d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "134 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/440200131"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgMCpq7izivBAEAMaCDYwMTAwMjMzIOndm4AGMBc41xBABXIJNDQwMjAwMTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"typ